reviewText: Was so much like other near death experience documentaries that I have watched. Just confirms to me the validity  of the experience.
Very interesting DVD to watch and understand more clearly eternal life.
If you are asking yourself this question then these DVD's are for you.  Pay close attention to the satanist's story!!!!!!

I do believe in life after death and we either go to Heaven or Hell, and I had seen the movie Heaven is for real and heard all the disclaimers about not being able to see them and then return to our bodies. I wanted to see what CBN had to say about it.  I know a person who had this experience before their actual death, about 10 years ago.  I believe we only have ourselves and unbelief will put us in the pit.  Accept Jesus, Follow God's Holy Word, Jesus bore our sins at the cross.
great information. Stories are good. This is a must see set of dvd's. This is not the entire movie on this dvd but the stories are still interesting.
